                            text="&lt;div class=&quot;ArticleContent&quot;>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;>&lt;img alt=&quot;fair play&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/images/news/Logo-XXV-edizione-FP-web.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:91px; width:300px&quot; title=&quot;fair play&quot; />&lt;/p>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:130%&quot;>The annual event dedicated to the high-standing values of ethics and fair play will be held in Florence and Castiglion Fiorentino from 30 August to 1 September 2021&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;p>01/04/21 &amp;ndash; The organization of the &lt;strong>25th International Fair Play-Menarini Awards&lt;/strong> has officially begun. &amp;nbsp;This year&amp;rsquo;s edition takes on even more significance with the 25-year anniversary celebration of the prestigious sporting event dedicated to the values of fair play, tolerance and solidarity. &amp;nbsp;The 2021 edition will in fact bring the biggest names in international sport to the Tuscan towns of Florence and Castiglion Fiorentino with a series of events and initiatives scheduled from Monday, 30 August to Wednesday, 1 September. &amp;nbsp;The choice to postpone the event until the end of summer was a deliberate one, not only in consideration of the Tokyo Olympic Games but also of the greater diffusion of the vaccination campaign.&lt;/p>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;p>For nine years, the &lt;strong>Menarini Pharmaceutical Group&lt;/strong> has supported the awards as title sponsor, thus associating its name with the shared values of ethics and fair play.&lt;/p>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/images/news/premiazione-finale-PFPM-2020-web.jpg&quot; style=&quot;height:375px; width:500px&quot; title=&quot;&quot; />&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;/div>"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
